          <i class="icon far fa-check-circle"></i>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Bespoke service</h3>
          <p>We provide a premium mortgage service for high net worth clients, working quickly and discreetly to achieve your desired outcome</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-10 col-sm-6 col-lg-5 mb-4">
      <div class="d-flex">
        <i class="icon far fa-lightbulb"></i>
        <div>
          <h3>Specialist knowledge</h3>
          <p>For our expert brokers, no situation is too complicated – our market knowledge means we find solutions where others can’t</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-10 col-sm-6 col-lg-5 mb-4">
      <div class="d-flex">
        <div>
          <i class="icon fas fa-handshake"></i>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Industry relationships</h3>
          <p>We have exceptional lender relationships across the UK and globally, enabling us to negotiate the best mortgage rates for your situation</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-10 col-sm-6 col-lg-5 mb-4">
      <div class="d-flex">
        <i class="icon fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
